  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether multi-convergent therapy is helpful to
      patients with inflammatory bowel disease who have functional abdominal symptoms or high
      perceived levels of psychological stress.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
